| notify.rs | `notify_immediate_when_dst_receiving` | matches WILLRECEIVE: dst.deliver_msg.m_type == NOTIFY_MESSAGE, dst unblocked. |
| notify.rs | `notify_defers_via_pending_bit` | dst not receiving: dst.priv.notify_pending bit for caller.priv.id set. |
| notify.rs | `notify_never_blocks_returns_ok` | caller.rts unchanged. |
| deadlock.rs | `size_two_send_recv_pair_is_legal` | caller wants SEND, dst is RECEIVING → `false`. |
| deadlock.rs | `size_three_cycle_detected` | A→SEND→B→SEND→C→SEND→A → `true`. |
| deadlock.rs | `noncyclic_chain_returns_false` | A→SEND→B (B unblocked) → `false`. |
| deadlock.rs | `self_send_is_deadlock` | A→SEND→A trivially → `true`. |
| mod.rs   | `do_ipc_etrapdenied_on_trap_mask_violation` | caller's `trap_mask` bit for SEND is clear → `ETRAPDENIED` returned in `frame.x[0]`. |
